name: Test Pilot - GWJ 34
description:
Endless "runner" (flyer?) for the Godot Wild Jam #34. This jam is normally a 9-day jam, but it ended up being a 12-hour jam for me.

Theme: Space

Wildcard: What's up Doc? - Add some carrots in your game (health, power-up, ammo, etc)

All 3D assets are made using Godot's internal primitives and materials

Textures made with MS Paint

Music from opengameart.org
SFX from freesound.org
